### Test WhatsApp API - Send Interactive Message with URL Button
POST https://graph.facebook.com/v23.0/{{$dotenv WHATSAPP_PHONE_NUMBER_ID}}/messages
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv WHATSAPP_TOKEN}}

{
  "messaging_product": "whatsapp",
  "to": "{{phoneNumber}}",
  "type": "template",
  "template": {
    "name": "support_button_he",
    "language": {
      "code": "he"
    },
    "components": [
      {
        "type": "body" 
      }
    ]
  }
}

